<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: both; border: solid #964B00; border-width: 1px 1px 0; background: #228B22; color: white; padding: .1em;padding-top: .1em;padding-left: .1em;padding-right: .1em;padding-bottom: .1em;text-align: center;font-family: sans-serif;font-size:100%;margin-bottom: 0px;">
<div class="plainlinks" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;font-size:80%; color: white"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Portal_Horse_racing_Did_you_know&action=edit.php.html"><span style="color: white">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;</div>
<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:white;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Did_you_know..."><i>Did you know...</i></span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #964B00; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #f9f9ff;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<ul>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that although the <a href="Quarter_Horse" title="Quarter Horse" class="mw-redirect">Quarter Horse</a> <b><a href="Lightning_Bar" title="Lightning Bar">Lightning Bar</a></b> is known as a racehorse and father of racehorses, he won a <a href="Team_Roping" title="Team Roping" class="mw-redirect">roping</a> contest once?</li>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that <b><a href="McDynamo" title="McDynamo">McDynamo</a></b> won the Grade 1 <a href="Breeders'_Cup_Grand_National_Steeplechase" title="Breeders' Cup Grand National Steeplechase">Breeders' Cup Grand National Steeplechase</a> in five consecutive years, with the fifth win coming as a 10-year-old, the oldest horse running that day?</li>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that early favorites in the <b><a href="2009_Kentucky_Derby" title="2009 Kentucky Derby">2009 Kentucky Derby</a></b> include the <a href="Filly" title="Filly">filly</a> <a href="Stardom_Bound" title="Stardom Bound">Stardom Bound</a>?
<table class="noprint" width="100%" border="0" style="padding: 0; margin: 0; background-color:transparent">
<tr>
<td>
<div style="text-align:left;margin-bottom:0px;"><b><a href="Did_you_know/index.html" title="Portal:Horse racing/Did you know">...Archive/Nominations</a></b></div>
</td>
<td>
<div style="text-align:right;margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:0px;">
<p><b><a href="Wikipedia_Recent_additions" title="Wikipedia:Recent additions">Read more...</a></b></p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class="noprint" style="text-align:right; margin:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; padding:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em;"></div>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div style="clear: both; border: solid #964B00; border-width: 1px 1px 0; background: #228B22; color: white; padding: .1em;padding-top: .1em;padding-left: .1em;padding-right: .1em;padding-bottom: .1em;text-align: center;font-family: sans-serif;font-size:100%;margin-bottom: 0px;">
