</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #964B00; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #f9f9ff;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;"><b><a href="http://en.wikinews.org/wiki/Portal:Horse_racing/Wikipedia" class="extiw" title="wikinews:Portal:Horse racing/Wikipedia">Wikinews Horse racing portal</a></b>
